typeProperties.script:
source(output(
		payment_type as short,
		abbreviation as string,
		description as string
	),
	allowSchemaDrift: false,
	validateSchema: false,
	ignoreNoFilesFound: false) ~> StagingPaymentType
source(output(
		LocationID as short,
		Borough as string,
		Zone as string,
		service_zone as string
	),
	allowSchemaDrift: true,
	validateSchema: false,
	ignoreNoFilesFound: false) ~> StagingTaxiZone
source(output(
		Trip_Month as string,
		Month_Name_Short as string,
		Month_Name_Full as string
	),
	allowSchemaDrift: true,
	validateSchema: false,
	ignoreNoFilesFound: false) ~> StagingTripMonth
source(output(
		trip_type as string,
		description as string
	),
	allowSchemaDrift: true,
	validateSchema: false,
	ignoreNoFilesFound: false) ~> StagingTripType
source(output(
		vendor_id as short,
		abbreviation as string,
		description as string
	),
	allowSchemaDrift: true,
	validateSchema: false,
	ignoreNoFilesFound: false) ~> StagingVendor
source(output(
		rate_code_id as short,
		description as string
	),
	allowSchemaDrift: true,
	validateSchema: false,
	ignoreNoFilesFound: false) ~> StagingRateCode
StagingPaymentType sink(allowSchemaDrift: true,
	validateSchema: false,
	format: 'parquet',
	preCommands: [],
	postCommands: []) ~> RawPaymentType
StagingRateCode sink(allowSchemaDrift: true,
	validateSchema: false,
	format: 'parquet',
	preCommands: [],
	postCommands: []) ~> RawRateCode
StagingTaxiZone sink(allowSchemaDrift: true,
	validateSchema: false,
	format: 'parquet',
	preCommands: [],
	postCommands: []) ~> RawTaxiZone
StagingTripMonth sink(allowSchemaDrift: true,
	validateSchema: false,
	format: 'parquet',
	preCommands: [],
	postCommands: []) ~> RawTripMonth
StagingTripType sink(allowSchemaDrift: true,
	validateSchema: false,
	format: 'parquet',
	preCommands: [],
	postCommands: []) ~> RawTripType
StagingVendor sink(allowSchemaDrift: true,
	validateSchema: false,
	format: 'parquet',
	preCommands: [],
	postCommands: []) ~> RawVendor
